name: Curupira
description: Known as the "forest demon", it whistles and uses false signals. It gathers many stories that involve inexplicable mysteries, for example, the disappearance of hunters, as well as forgetting the paths. They say that with their feet turned back, Curupira deceives and confuses people who damage their habitat, for example, hunters, loggers and woodcutters. <Crypto Legends | A Series by Renancio Monte | 2021>
